articles.title: Japan's Toshiba set to end 74-year stock market history - BBC
articles.description: A group of investors plans to take the company private after buying more than 78% of its shares.
articles.content:
Toshiba, one of Japan's oldest and biggest firms, is set to end its 74-year stock market history as a group of investors have bought a majority stake.
